citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:45 pm on
08-Jun-17.
The inspector arrived at the facility and spoke to a household member who stated the licensee was not available for
the inspection. The inspector also called the licensee's phone and left a message.
